snippet.title: ASCENXION - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
ASCENXION is a 2D shoot 'em up game where you explore the field to progress. Players must overcome puzzles, traps, elite units, boss fights, and other various obstacles while navigating the field. Grow stronger through rewards earned, to uncover the truth of this world.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1000000/ASCENXION/

ASCENXION © 2021 IndigoBlue Game Studio. Soundtrack produced by IndigoBlue & HaWul. Distributed by PsychoFlux Entertainment. All rights reserved.
